by Pwn3r1001
Brought to you by Dooz Mapping Studio @ http://www.fpsbanana.com/studios/1229
release: July 10 2007
pwner1001@hotmail.com
LORDSOFWARCLAN.ORG



Description
***********
This is one of my quick maps, mainly a sniper map hence the name aim_tower_sniper. The huge displacements are used for cover when crossing to the other side or to the tower. There's awps and scouts at each team's spawn points. There's semi-auto rifles inside the tower. Enjoy!

Required
********
Counter-strike:Source.

Installation
************
Download the file, extract the aim_tower_sniper.bsp file to  steam/steamapps/{yourusername}/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps/


Uninstall
*********
Just delete the map.

Usage
*****
You can test the map by going to start a new server in CS:S then pick the map and start. 

Admins
******
I would suggest using bzipper from here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/tools/1495 . Extract the .bsp into the folder and use the bzipper tool to compress. Then take that compressed file and put it into your map folder in your server( usually at C:\Program Files\Valve\HLServer\cstrike\maps) or if your using a webserver for downloads it's the same idea. Also add aim_tower_sniper to maplist.txt in your server folder.

Mappers
*******
If you would like to customize/modify aim_tower_sniper email me at pwner1001@hotmail.com and I'll be glad to give you the .vmf as long as you give proper credit to my name in the readme and installer if you make one. 
 

Thanks to
*********
Valve for all models, and hammer editor to make map.

Pretty much an FY map made of dev textures with a bombsite.  The secret code for the Super secret room is 0419.  Keep it to yourself, share it, whatever.  There's a tele to the sniper box in there, that cant be seen outside, but you can see out and snipe people.  If you get the code wrong, then you go to jail.  There's an escape button, that will tele you out after 15 seconds.  The buttons on the towers will destroy the spawn kill protect glass after 30 seconds of being pressed.  Enjoy!

Had fun making this map, this map works well with bots..... sorta... they really do suck with ladders.......

Novelties :

- There are not walls anymore by which we can see through and fire.
- The lights of the small towers are already switched off and buttons were deleted.
- We can now fire on the button of gases and on the big red buttons, which activate too gases.
- When gases are activated, railings traps the player in the room down.
- There are flashes of lighting which touch the lightning conductor and electrify the ground down from the big tower.
- Footbridges enter the big tower and 4 small towers are anymore visible and are better protected.
- Traps are actionable (by firing on 3 buttons) at the top of every footbridge and which make roll a big coal nut on the aimed footbridge. Furthermore, these coal nuts block the access of footbridges when they arrive in the rear.
- There is a big subterranean creusable gallery, like "Minecraft"!
- Below the map, there is a new danger zone with the lava and numerous automatic traps!
- There is a teleport below the map (in the zone of lava) which brings the player at the top of the main tower. As soon as the player touches this new teleport, a flash of lighting appears and electrifies the ground down from the main tower.
- At the top of the main tower, there is 2 awp, 4 smokes and 4 small zones where we can better see the rest of the map.
- The lighting of the map was improved, but with a darker sky.

We can buy weapons to the beginning of all rounds. There are a lot of traversables walls by which we can see and fire. Buttons serve to switch off lights of every tower. Also a button allows to activate the toxic steam in the room of the main tower. Invisible footbridges allow to go at the top of the main tower, via 4 other towers.
